title: Gay - TylersRoom - Brayden and Morgan
description: Brayden and Morgan Age: 19 and 23 Description: I'd like to welcome Morgan back as well as a newcomer to Tylers Room, Brayden. Brayden is a versatile top who was more than willing to bottom for this set. He's 19 and from Iowa and Morgan is 23 from Wisconsin. While Morgan has been in the industry for quite a few years Brayden is just getting started out. :)
